In Lesson Two, Supply Chain Management Objectives,

2
00:00:03.953 --> 00:00:05.682
we are going to learn that the goals

3
00:00:05.682 --> 00:00:08.404
of supply chain management are to create value

4
00:00:08.404 --> 00:00:10.274
through financial benefits,

5
00:00:10.274 --> 00:00:12.896
add value for customers and stakeholders,

6
00:00:12.896 --> 00:00:14.805
improve customer service,

7
00:00:14.805 --> 00:00:17.979
and effectively and efficiently use resources.

8
00:00:17.979 --> 00:00:21.655
In healthcare, there are requirements must be met

9
00:00:21.655 --> 00:00:23.424
in order to deliver care to the patients

10
00:00:23.424 --> 00:00:25.594
in the safest manner possible.

11
00:00:25.594 --> 00:00:28.362
These requirements, detailed next,

12
00:00:28.362 --> 00:00:31.043
must be understood and upheld by all.

